675
01:11:41,458 --> 01:11:43,083
<i>Alright, miss.</i>

676
01:11:44,250 --> 01:11:47,583
<i>Then, you only have tonight to do it.</i>

677
01:11:49,333 --> 01:11:51,416
<i>And no one else should see it.</i>

678
01:11:52,041 --> 01:11:53,708
